span.p:
Manual:
Load workpiece to Three-in-one station;
Connect workpiece male connector with female coupler;
Press start button

Automatic:
Vent N2;
Evacuate the workpiece;
Charge Helium

Manual:
Load workpiece into chamber;
Press start button

Automatic:
Chamber door close;
Evacuate chamber to below 30 Pa

Manual:
Connect workpiece male connector with female coupler at Helium recovery station;
Press start button
